name: FRIDAY PRAYER the 5th
description:
We have finally arrived at the end of the odyssey of prayers (2021).
This figure has appeared in 2019 with the "kneeling" format as my independent t-shirt DIY merchandise (@st.elsel).

The selection of this pop culture figure is a tribute to the western world (Europe) who has succeeded in using elements of religion into commercial products in a genius, smooth, and fun way for all ages since 1820 in USA malls. The power of the media and buying demand was the perfect combination to introduce this red-clad bearded Caucasian old man to the world.

After everything you've witnessed, you knew he was going to show up, right?
 
Anyway, Merry Christmas my brothers and sisters around the world. SPREADS LOVE. XoXo.

schedule: mint on friday, burn on next thursday
